Detect Disobedience	KEY:Trait ~ Detect Disobedience		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.SocialTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.SocialTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Detect Disobedience]						DESC:You gain a +2 bonus on Sense Motive checks to detect when an underling is trying to hide something from you, and can attempt such checks instead of Perception checks to notice and react to a subordinate's surprise attack against you.																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.7
Horrifying Mind		KEY:Trait ~ Horrifying Mind			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.MagicTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.MagicTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Horrifying Mind]							DESC:When a nonevil humanoid attempts to read your mind via a magical effect, the reader must attempt a Will save opposed by your Wisdom or Charisma check (your choice). If the reader fails this save, she is shaken for 1 round. If she fails by 10 or more, she is instead frightened for 1 round, then shaken for 1 round.																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Passionate Inertia	KEY:Trait ~ Passionate Inertia		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.SocialTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.SocialTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Passionate Inertia]						DESC:You gain a +2 bonus on Will saves to resist having your mind changed about something, but you take a -1 penalty on Will saves to resist temptation and compulsions you might reasonably be already inclined toward.																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.11
Punish Insurrection	KEY:Trait ~ Punish Insurrection		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Punish Insurrection]						DESC:Against members of the same organization who formally answer to you, you gain a +1 bonus on attack and damage rolls. You also gain this bonus against members who have openly defied the authority or rules of that body, provided that their standing is now less than yours.																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.7
Subjective Truth		KEY:Trait ~ Subjective Truth			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.SocialTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.SocialTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Subjective Truth]						DESC:You gain a +2 bonus on Bluff checks to lie, provided the person you're lying to has never known you to lie to him. Failing this check counts as being caught in a lie by the target, negating any future use of this bonus against that person.																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Wicked Leader		KEY:Trait ~ Wicked Leader			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.SocialTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.SocialTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Wicked Leader]							DESC:You gain a +1 bonus on Charisma checks against evil creatures. If you select the Leadership feat or the Vile Leadership feat at any point when you meet the prerequisites for that feat, you can recruit a cohort who is up to 1 level lower than you (instead of the normal requirement) as long as your cohort is evil.																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.12

Divine Deceiver		KEY:Trait ~ Divine Deceiver			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RegionalTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Divine Deceiver]		PREREGION:Razmiran	DESC:Once per day as a full-round action, you can sacrifice a prepared arcane spell or spell slot to manifest healing magic. This acts as cure light wounds, except you heal 1d6 points of damage per level of the spell or spell slot sacrificed (maximum 5d6) and the hit points healed are temporary (lasting 1 hour).																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.13
Obsequious Morsel		KEY:Trait ~ Obsequious Morsel			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RegionalTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Obsequious Morsel]		PREREGION:Geb		DESC:Once per day as a swift action, you can use sanctuary as a spell-like ability (caster level = your highest caster level, or 1st if you have no caster level), with a DC of %1. Only undead must save to attack you (other creature types are not affected). The effect ends as soon as you attack a creature, as normal.|10+floor(CASTERLEVEL/2)+CHA																															SOURCEPAGE:p.12
Shadowsight			KEY:Trait ~ Shadowsight				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RegionalTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Shadowsight]			PREREGION:Nidal		DESC:As a swift action once per day, your eyes can pierce the surrounding darkness-you gain the benefit of lowlight vision for %1 rounds.|TL																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.13
Social Slaver		KEY:Trait ~ Social Slaver			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RegionalTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Social Slaver]			PREREGION:Cheliax		DESC:You gain a +2 bonus on Intimidate checks against creatures one or more size categories smaller than yourself. The DC of compulsion spells cast by you against smaller creatures increases by 1.																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.12
Wardbreaker			KEY:Trait ~ Wardbreaker				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RegionalTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Wardbreaker]			PREREGION:Worldwound	DESC:Once per day, you can attempt a melee touch attack against an opponent that you believe has a deflection bonus to AC. If your attack is successful, your foe's deflection bonus to AC is halved (to a minimum of +0) for %1 rounds. You can use this ability twice per day at 10th level and three times per day at 20th level.|CHA																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.13


