Foul Brand			KEY:Drawback ~ Foul Brand			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Drawback				PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Drawback],[PREVAREQ:BypassDrawbackRestriction,1],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Drawback ~ Foul Brand]							DESC:You have the symbol of an evil deity burned into your flesh. If the symbol is on your hand, you take a -1 penalty on Disable Device, Disguise, and Sleight of Hand checks. If the symbol is on your face, you take a -2 penalty on Bluff, Diplomacy, and Disguise checks. This does not count as a holy symbol for the purposes of a divine focus for spellcasting.																										COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
Umbral Unmasking		KEY:Drawback ~ Umbral Unmasking		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Drawback				PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Drawback],[PREVAREQ:BypassDrawbackRestriction,1],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Drawback ~ Umbral Unmasking]						DESC:You cast no shadow whatsoever, or the shadow you do have is monstrous. Under normal lighted conditions, this is not hard to observe-but uncommon to notice. Creatures that succeed at a DC 15 Wisdom check notice it plainly (an additional Perception check may be required based on environmental conditions). This telltale sign of wickedness cannot be concealed, except those effects that also affect shadows (such as invisibility).														COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
Warded Against Nature	KEY:Drawback ~ Warded Against Nature	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Drawback				PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Drawback],[PREVAREQ:BypassDrawbackRestriction,1],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Drawback ~ Warded Against Nature]					DESC:Animals do not willingly approach within 30 feet of you, unless you or the animal's master succeeds at a DC 20 Handle Animal, Ride, or wild empathy check. Animal companions, familiars, and mounts granted by your class abilities are immune to this effect.																																											COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
